server.controller

Class PrepareDataForClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.controller.PrepareDataForClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PrepareDataForClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class reads the state of the game and saves it in different elementary structures as array or variable. In this way CLI or GUI don't need to know the complex model in the server
